description: Spain, Germany and Italy are also seeing their highest daily case numbers for months.
title: France: Virus cases spike to 4,700 in a day
title_page: France: Virus cases spike to 4,700 in a day - BBC News
maintext: France has increased its testing capacity and carried out 664,000 tests over the past week, the health ministry said, but the rate of positive cases has also been increasing. It stood at 3.3% for the week between 11-17 August, up from 2.1% previously and more than double the 1.5% rate seen at the end of July.
